CustomField.description: Parameter to allow the optimizer to change strategies starting from a percentage of time allocated. Value is a number in the range 0.0-1.0. 0.75 means this strategy would be used in the last 75% of the allocated time.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Parameter to allow the optimizer to change strategies starting from a percentage of time allocated. Value is a number in the range 0.0-1.0. 0.75 means this strategy would be used in the last 75% of the allocated time.
CustomField.label: ShakeOff Time Ratio
